    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is primarily recommended for someone looking for a project or a source for parts. The engine starts but suffers from a heavy oil leak and a persistent misfire, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping between gears. Externally, there is significant rust on the rocker panels and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. It will require substantial mechanical work and cosmetic attention before it can be reliably driven on the road.",
