    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in commendable condition, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience backed by a history of dedicated maintenance. Every aspect of this automobile has been carefully preserved to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. It features a refined interior and a robust powertrain, representing a superior choice for the professional seeking both performance and longevity. This is an investment-grade vehicle that delivers exceptional value and enduring style.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been well-cared for\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great on the road. I've loved every mile in it, and I'm sure you will too! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, powered by the sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW rotary engine. This vehicle features a precise five-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, maintaining the iconic 50/50 weight distribution that defines this chassis. The sequential turbo transition remains seamless, with the secondary compressor engaging smoothly under load. Recent technical updates include a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator and a comprehensive inspection of the complex vacuum 'rat's nest' to ensure optimal boost pressure. The suspension geometry is stock and tight, providing the high-frequency feedback and razor-sharp turn-in expected from this platform. A well-sorted example of Japanese forced-induction engineering.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Reliable performance. Clean title. Maintenance records available.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior maintains a lustrous shine, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seats remain soft and supportive, with only slight creasing on the driver-side bolster. All interior technology, including the infotainment screen and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change and brake pad replacement completed just last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the engine delivers smooth, consistent power without any unusual noises. This is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready to be driven home today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. Featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning motorist. We invite you to experience the superior handling and reliable engineering of this exceptional automotive offering.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in great shape for its next adventure! It runs smoothly, has been well-cared for, and is super comfortable for both daily commutes and weekend road trips. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.8L M97.01 flat-six powerplant with VarioCam Plus. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring under load. Recent maintenance includes a preventative IMS bearing retrofit and a clean bore-scoping report, confirming the integrity of the Nikasil-coated cylinder walls. The Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) provides active damping adjustment, while the braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors for consistent thermal management. Though the exterior reflects its 'good' status with honest patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the Rear Main Seal (RMS) and AOS\u2014are robust. It sits on staggered alloys wrapped in high-performance rubber, offering exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
